headline: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish on Church & Dwight Stock?
summary: While Church & Dwight has underperformed the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.

headline: Rothschild & Co Upgrades Church & Dwight Co to Neutral, Raises Price Target to $91
summary: Rothschild & Co  analyst Edward Lewis   upgrades Church & Dwight Co (NYSE:CHD) from Sell to Neutral and raises the price target from $81 to $91.
